:<font size="15">מגדּלה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
מגדּלה   - מגדּל / migdâl  migdâlâh / mig-dawl', mig-daw-law'

===Etymology===
From [[גּדל]] {{HH|1431}}; a tower (from its size or height); by analogy a rostrum; figuratively a (pyramidal) bed of flowers

===Noun===
'''מגדּלה'''

# A castle, flower, pulpit, tower. Compare the names following.

